00:18:39,856 --> 00:18:41,076
it's definitely missing.

436
00:18:41,176 --> 00:18:43,677
So it doesn't feel quite as exciting

437
00:18:43,737 --> 00:18:45,878
for that initial part of the power deployment there.

438
00:18:45,998 --> 00:18:49,039
But at the same time, the game runs cross-platform.

439
00:18:49,479 --> 00:18:50,941
A lot of folks are enjoying it that way.

440
00:18:51,201 --> 00:18:53,403
It feels fair because you have the same targeting mechanisms

441
00:18:53,443 --> 00:18:56,046
for both games, both versions of the game.

442
00:18:56,666 --> 00:18:59,169
And one of our main requests that we get from our community

443
00:18:59,229 --> 00:19:00,650
is for more cross-play.

444
00:19:00,910 --> 00:19:03,433
So at the end of the day, this is also another trade-off

445
00:19:03,513 --> 00:19:05,395
where, well, it feels like something was lost.

446
00:19:05,455 --> 00:19:06,336
We gain something else.

447
00:19:10,015 --> 00:19:13,203
So as we think about the various takeaways from the game

448
00:19:13,244 --> 00:19:16,251
and what this iterative process brought us,

449
00:19:16,391 --> 00:19:18,116
here's a few things that we would probably take

450
00:19:18,156 --> 00:19:19,279
from one game to another.

451
00:19:21,136 --> 00:19:23,437
So the first one here is know your core, right.

452
00:19:23,637 --> 00:19:25,718
And so for us, yes, we've got a lot of history

453
00:19:25,738 --> 00:19:27,099
in terms of what the franchise is,

454
00:19:27,579 --> 00:19:29,960
but how that applies to each game is a bit unique.

455
00:19:30,501 --> 00:19:31,921
And it's important for us to make sure

456
00:19:31,941 --> 00:19:34,563
that we're constantly reevaluating what that means,

457
00:19:35,143 --> 00:19:38,004
updating our internal documentation and specs for that,

458
00:19:38,104 --> 00:19:39,825
and really just thinking about how it applies

459
00:19:39,905 --> 00:19:40,726
to that new title.

